    <td width="670" background="images/table_header.jpg"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><b>He Is Dead!!!!!! So Damn Dead!!  (c) Haro</b><br>Monday, January 01, 05:08 -- Posted by: Stekarn</font></td>
